// OpenBox.astro — Celulares Open Box · Minimal · Steel / Olive
---

<section id="open-box" class="ob-section">
  <div class="ob-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="ob-grain"></div>
    <div class="ob-line ob-line-top"></div>
    <div class="ob-line ob-line-bottom"></div>
    <span class="ob-watermark">OPEN BOX</span>
  </div>

  <div class="ob-inner">
    <!-- ── HEADER ── -->
